    # "We don't talk much as I drive her back home."
    "On ne parle pas beaucoup pendant que je la ramène chez elle."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:13
translate french maridateendbad_332660ab:

    # "When I pull in, I look over at her."
    "Quand je me gare, je la regarde."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:14
translate french maridateendbad_f2749287:

    # pc "I'm sorry about today."
    pc "Je suis désolé pour aujourd’hui."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:15
translate french maridateendbad_32607601:

    # fr "Yeah."
    fr "Ouais."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:16
translate french maridateendbad_e2f49b67:

    # fr "I don't think I want to see you anymore."
    fr "Je crois que je ne veux plus te voir."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:17
translate french maridateendbad_364fcd03:

    # fr "Bye, [pcname]."
    fr "Au revoir, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:18
translate french maridateendbad_51f7879e:

    # "With that, she gets out of the car and walk into her house."
    "Sur ces mots, elle sort de la voiture et entre chez elle."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:22
translate french maridateendbad_d0cc2cdb:

    # "I drive out of her driveway and back towards town."
    "Je sors de son allée et reprends la route vers la ville."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:23
translate french maridateendbad_fb9b9632:

    # "I guess Mari and I are done. I'd have to do something pretty big to get her to even talk to me again."
    "Je suppose que c'est fini entre Mari et moi. Il faudrait que je fasse quelque chose d'assez spectaculaire pour qu'elle daigne me parler à nouveau."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:33
translate french maridateendpoor_fda24b08:

    # "We don't talk much as I drive her back home."
    "On ne parle pas beaucoup pendant que je la ramène chez elle."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:37
translate french maridateendpoor_0a3401a5:

    # "I pull into her driveway and park near her door."
    "Je m'engage dans son allée et me gare près de sa porte."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:38
translate french maridateendpoor_54cc5537:

    # pc "I'm sorry today wasn't great."
    pc "Je suis désolé que ça se soit pas très bien passé aujourd'hui."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:39
translate french maridateendpoor_96ff618e:

    # fr "Yeah, it could have gone better."
    fr "Ouais, ça aurait pu mieux se passer."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:40
translate french maridateendpoor_86900206:

    # fr "Still, it wasn't awful. I'd go out again with you sometime if you wanted."
    fr "Mais bon, c'était pas si terrible. Je ressortirais bien avec toi un de ces jours si tu veux."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:44
translate french maridateendpoor_025a1db1:

    # fr "Okay. Well call me sometime then."
    fr "D'accord. Appelle-moi un de ces jours, alors."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:45
translate french maridateendpoor_9f231683:

    # pc "I will. See you later."
    pc "Je le ferai. À plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:46
translate french maridateendpoor_79ef1b9c:

    # fr "Bye."
    fr "Au revoir."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:47
translate french maridateendpoor_9a02741f:

    # "With that, she gets out of the car and walks up to her door."
    "Sur ces mots, elle sort de la voiture et se dirige vers sa porte."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:51
translate french maridateendpoor_b5a7fa55:

    # "It hadn't been the best date, but it wasn't too bad either. At least she agreed to go on another with me."
    "Ce n'était pas le meilleur des rendez-vous, mais ce n'était pas si mal non plus. Au moins, elle a accepté de sortir à nouveau avec moi."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:52
translate french maridateendpoor_80af0e20:

    # "I'll just have to make the next one better."
    "Je vais juste devoir faire en sorte que le prochain soit meilleur."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:57
translate french maridateendpoor_7a7f5252:

    # fr "Okay. Well thanks for taking me out."
    fr "D'accord. Eh bien, merci de m'avoir invitée."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:58
translate french maridateendpoor_e00118b5:

    # fr "I hope you find somebody that you fit with better."
    fr "J'espère que tu trouveras quelqu'un qui te correspond mieux."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:59
translate french maridateendpoor_eb61ef6e:

    # pc "You too."
    pc "Toi aussi."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:60
translate french maridateendpoor_1454e679:

    # "With that, she steps out of the car and walks up to her door."
    "Sur ces mots, elle sort de la voiture et se dirige vers sa porte."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:66
translate french maridateendpoor_0ca75f3a:

    # "That hadn't gone as well as I would have liked, but at least Mari doesn't hate me, I guess?"
    "Ça ne s'est pas passé aussi bien que je l'aurais souhaité, mais au moins Mari ne me déteste pas, j'imagine ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:67
translate french maridateendpoor_9b418399:

    # "We just don't work together well. There's others out there."
    "On ne s'entend tout simplement pas bien ensemble. Il y a d'autres personnes."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:75
translate french maridateendgood_9201f7f4:

    # "We don't talk much during the drive."
    "On ne parle pas beaucoup pendant le trajet."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:79
translate french maridateendgood_2759b5c3:

    # "When I pull into her driveway, I look over at her."
    "Quand je m'engage dans son allée, je la regarde."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:80
translate french maridateendgood_84e51ab3:

    # pc "This was fun. I hope you had a good time."
    pc "C'était sympa. J'espère que tu as passé un bon moment."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:82
translate french maridateendgood_68ef2b7a:

    # fr "I did, definitely."
    fr "Oui, sans aucun doute."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:83
translate french maridateendgood_6a7e81c5:

    # fr "I can't wait to do it again."
    fr "J'ai hâte de recommencer."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:84
translate french maridateendgood_d97139f0:

    # fr "Walk me up to the door?"
    fr "Tu m'accompagnes jusqu'à la porte ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:85
translate french maridateendgood_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:86
translate french maridateendgood_0d361a68:

    # "I park the car in her driveway and walk with her up to her front door."
    "Je gare la voiture dans son allée et je l'accompagne jusqu'à sa porte d'entrée."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:93
translate french maridateendgood_1ff3de05:

    # fr "I had a really good time. We'll do this again soon right?"
    fr "J'ai vraiment passé un bon moment. On recommencera bientôt, n'est-ce pas ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:94
translate french maridateendgood_4664af7e:

    # pc "For sure."
    pc "C'est sûr."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:95
translate french maridateendgood_40ea4840:

    # fr "Okay. Well I'll see you later then."
    fr "D'accord. Eh bien, à plus tard alors."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:100
translate french maridateendgood_01cc1a36:

    # "I lean in and kiss her. She kisses back enthusiastically."
    "Je me penche vers elle et l'embrasse. Elle me rend mon baiser avec enthousiasme."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:101
translate french maridateendgood_7d104398:

    # "We stay like that for some time, our lips locked, our tongues exploring each other."
    "Nous restons ainsi un moment, nos lèvres scellées, nos langues s'explorant mutuellement."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:102
translate french maridateendgood_ec427365:

    # "I want to take it further, but then she pulls away."
    "Je voudrais aller plus loin, mais elle s'écarte soudain."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:105
translate french maridateendgood_77fea71d:

    # fr "Woah. As nice as that is, we need to stop."
    fr "Ouah. C'est très agréable, mais il faut qu'on s'arrête."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:106
translate french maridateendgood_f6edb1e6:

    # fr "You better go, but I look forward to continuing this later."
    fr "Tu ferais mieux d’y aller, mais j’ai hâte de continuer ça plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:107
translate french maridateendgood_191e3fc9:

    # fr "I'll see you again soon, okay?"
    fr "On se reverra bientôt, d’accord ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:108
translate french maridateendgood_a2cba356:

    # pc "Okay. Bye, Mari."
    pc "D’accord. Salut, Mari."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:109
translate french maridateendgood_364fcd03:

    # fr "Bye, [pcname]."
    fr "Salut, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:112
translate french maridateendgood_5de4b6b2:

    # "With that, she turns and walks inside and I go back to the car."
    "Sur ce, elle se retourne et rentre chez elle, et je retourne à la voiture."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:114
translate french maridateendgood_5c0b14bd:

    # "She gives me a final smile before turning and going inside the house."
    "Elle m’adresse un dernier sourire avant de se retourner et d’entrer dans la maison."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:117
translate french maridateendgood_550f3dd4:

    # "I walk back to the car."
    "Je retourne à la voiture."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/marienddate.rpy:121
translate french maridateendgood_1fa2fe2f:

    # "The whole way back to town, all I can think about is our next date."
    "Pendant tout le trajet de retour en ville, je ne pense qu’à notre prochain rendez-vous."

